org.opends.server.core

Class CompareOperationBasis

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.types.AbstractOperation
      • org.opends.server.core.CompareOperationBasis
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, CompareOperation, Operation, PluginOperation, PostResponseCompareOperation, PostResponseOperation, PreParseCompareOperation, PreParseOperation

    public class CompareOperationBasis
extends AbstractOperation
implements PreParseCompareOperation, CompareOperation, PostResponseCompareOperation
    This class defines an operation that may be used to determine whether a specified entry in the Directory Server contains a given attribute-value pair.
